DESCRIPTION:Allen Noftall - Swallow Hill Production Manager – 303-875-017
 5 – allen@spacerecording.com
  Promoter Contact: Shauna Sweeney. Cell Number: 954-770-9473\n
  ** Tour - Artist arrival / parking address: 1001 York St.**\n
  Dressing Rooms: Dressing rooms are located approximately 150 yards from
  the stage. There is\n
  no backstage area due to the “in the round” logistics. Artist acces
 s to stage is a cement pathway\n
  through the audience (see photo above). We will supply security personn
 el to assist artist to and\n
  from stage.\n
  Mitchell Hall: Is where the dressing rooms / hospitality / “Green Roo
 m” areas are located.\n
  It is a large room (100’ x 100’) set up into 3 private areas (dress
 ing rooms) with pipe and\n
  drape. Each of these areas (10’ x 20’) has tables\, chairs and mirr
 ors. There is a large open\n
  area used for hospitality with tables and chairs. A production office c
 an also be setup in this\n
  area. This room has a security person stationed at main door and is not
  open to the public.\n
  No private restrooms directly in this area. Public restrooms are locate
 d across lobby. There\n
  are no showers\, laundry\, or office facilities. See layout below.\n
  Wi-Fi Information: Network Name- “DBG-PUB” -WiFi. Password- None.\n
  Promoter will also provide a tour “Hot Spot”. Network name and pass
 word will be provided\n
  DOS.\n
  ! Parking: Tour bus/vehicle parking is on the west side of York St. at
 front of venue in a parking\n
  lane located on west side of street. For GPS purposes\, this parking is
  at 1001 York St. There will beproduction staff available to help direct
  (See maps below). There is no shore power.\n
  ! Runner: We will have a runner with a 15-passenger van available all d
 ay for the tour’s use.\n
  \n*************************************\nSCHEDULE:\n
  12:00 PM PDT: Angie Load/ Console set up\n-----------------------------
 -----------\n
