  4 Directions\n
  LLORONA\n
  La Catrina stays on to address audience: WELCOME & Call Las Cafeteras t
 o stage\n
  Musicians enter to their station\n
  HECTOR LEADS:\n
  Season to remember (Dia de Muertos reminds us)\n
  -Where you From From (To know where you are going\, you have to know wh
 ere you come from)\n
  -Coco: Ultimate Death\n
  -ways to remember (food\, stories\,songs)\n
  CARAVANA\n
  Hector transitions about Art imitating life\, honoring the stories of o
 ur families to make sense of how to hold space for community- to hold ea
 ch other up and not be ashamed\n
