 3\n
  Map: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1qIKN_6StUsdSIbyOfI5fZfIRW3liBJjh/
 view?usp=sharing\n
  If there isnt anything to load\, go ahead and park in G3 and we will co
 me out to meet you at the ground floor of THE SORAYA complex and lead yo
 u upstairs.\n
  CALL MATT WHEN YOU ARRIVE: 661-305-3630\n
  With gps service\, you can simply put THE SOCAL SOUND in both Apple M
 aps and Google Maps\, and that will lead you to the correct location tha
 t corresponds with the map attached.\n
  It is most helpful to follow the red staggered line on the map attached
 . The easiest landmark to look out for is the 76 gas station that is adj
 acent to the university on Nordhoff and Lindley\, you will be making
 a right from Nordhoff onto Lindley towards the Information Booth #1. Whe
 n you are close\, Call Matt and I will head downstairs with a cart and h
 elp lead up from the loading location on the north side of the grey buil
 ding\, adjacent to the ‘Earthquake Garden’ found on the map attached
 .\n
  \nVENUE INFO:\n
    tel:+1 818-677-3090\n
