SUMMARY:DC/HF Radio Interview (Zoom)
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20250318T130000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20250318T130000
DESCRIPTION:Daybreak Star Radio
  Contact: Aiyana Irwin/ Production Assistant\n
  Here is the zoom link for todays interview : https://us06web.zoom.us/j
 /84758469065?pwd=f66bRZtVGgmnKIFWGeikTi3JDxslw2.1\n
  Questions will be things along the line of:\n
  When did you first discover your love of music?\n
  How did you come together to create your unique sound?\n
  How has you culture influenced your music?\n
  What do you hope your audiences take away from your music?\n
  Do you have any upcoming projects you can tell us about?\n
  What advice do you have for young Indigenous artists who want to create
  music?\n
  If you have any specific things you want to talk about let me know and
 we can make sure to add questions about them.\n
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CLASS:PUBLIC
CREATED:20250311T044626
LAST-MODIFIED:20250318T181530
