SUMMARY:DC/ HF UNIVISION INTERVIEW (live)
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20251013T123000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20251013T134500
DESCRIPTION:ARRIVAL TIME: 1 p.m.
  INTERVIEW START TIME: 1:10 p.m.\n
  CLEAR BY TIME: 1:30 p.m. at the very latest\n
  From ArtPower: Liz\, Alyssa\, and Connor will be on site to support any
  needs that Denise and Hector may have.\n
  Talking points:\n
  Tickets are available at artpower.ucsd.edu\n
  The venue’s full name is Epstein Family Amphitheater.\n
  Epstein rhythms with spleen\n
  Contacts for ArtPower:\n
  Alyssa: 760-693-3293\n
  Liz: 858-405-4589\n
  Connor: 760-470-0943\n
  SUGGESTED QUESTIONS:\n
  1.You’re back at UC San Diego for another performance with ArtPower
 – what keeps you coming back?\n
  2-How does Hasta La Muerte bring the celebration of Día De Los Muertos
  to life?\n
  3-Hasta La Muerte brings together so many forms of artistic expression\
 , from dance and musical performance to theatrical set pieces\, how do y
 ou bring all these elements together to form one\, cohesive piece?\n
  4-The entire performance is centered around themes of death\, grief\, a
 nd love. Are there any personal inspirations each of you have that fed i
 nto the creation of Hasta La\n
  Muerte?\n
  5-Part of this performance is a reimagining of traditional Mexican folk
 lore– how do you go about reimagining and reinterpreting that folklore
  while still keeping the legacy of those stories intact?\n
  \nVENUE INFO:\n
    tel:+1 858-576-1919\n
    http://www.univisionsandiego.com/\n
