 n side)\, Red Onion and Candied Walnuts\, House-made Gluten Friendly Cr
 outons\, and Peach Balsamic Vinaigrette (Gluten Friendly\, Vegetarian)\n
  Sourdough Baguette\, Herbed Focaccia\, and Naan with Olive Tapenade (Ve
 getarian)\n
