SUMMARY:ART TOWN (Reno\, NV)
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260722T150000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260722T230000
DESCRIPTION:Tenessa Ripple
  775-546-3319\n
  The Helaine Greenberg Stage at Rancho San Rafael Regional Park\n
  There are no private dressing rooms.\n
  There is one greenroom on one side of the stage and an artist's only ba
 throom with one stall on the other side of the stage.\n
  \nVENUE INFO:\n
    tel:+1 775-785-4512\n
    https://www.washoecounty.gov/parks/parks/park_directory_pages/north_r
 egion/rancho_san_rafael_regional_park.php\n
  \n*************************************\nSCHEDULE:\n
  2:30 PM - 5:00 PM PDT: Load/Soundcheck- CALL TENNESSA 775-546-3319\n
 No music during these time frames:\n
  4:15 pm-4:25 pm\n
  5:15 pm-5:25 pm\n
  6:15 pm-6:25 pm\n
  6:40 pm-6:55 pm\n
  When you arrive at the venue\, please follow the signs to the ADA parki
 ng lot. From there\, you will drive directly into the park to the green
 room area\, where parking is available for up to two vehicles.  Please g
 ive me a call when you arrive\, and I can meet you at the ADA parking lo
 t to guide you in. The route may feel unusual\, as you'll be driving alo
 ng a dirt path\, but that is the correct way to access the green room ar
 ea. (Tenessa Ripple)\n
  \n----------------------------------------\n
  5:00 PM - 7:00 PM PDT: DInner and Dress\n------------------------------
 ----------\n
  6:00 PM PDT: Doors\n----------------------------------------\n
  6:30 PM - 7:00 PM PDT: LIVE INTERVIEWS (by the stage)\n----------------
 ------------------------\n
  7:30 PM - 9:00 PM PDT: Showtime 90 min\n-------------------------------
 ---------\n
  \n*************************************\nACCOMMODATIONS:\n
    Reno Hotel: Circus Circus\n
    ARRIVE: 7/22/2026 3:00 PM PDT\n
    DEPART: 7/23/2026 8:00 AM PDT\n
    HOTEL ROOMING LIST\n
  DENISE CARLOS (SFDTM)\n
  HECTOR FLORES (6SPF5)\n
  ANGELA GONZALEZ (F3HWY)\n
  JORGE MIJANGOS/ JOHN CALANCHINI (YCRYT)\n
  MOISES BAQUEIRO/ JONNY JYEMO. (SMTZL)\n
  \n
    \n----------------------------------------\n
